Name: Source Area Name
Description: Name of Source Area (e.g. 'On Lot Landscaping')

Name: BMP Family
Description: Type of BMP Used for that Source Area

Name: BMP Volume
Description: Volume of BMP Used for that Source Area (ft3)

Name: Annual Runoff Volume
Description: Annual Runoff Volume from the Source Area Prior to Implementation of BMPs (normalized to an SLDM size of 1 acre) (ft3/SLDM-acre)

Name: Annual Runoff Volume Retained
Description: Annual Runoff Volume Captured by the BMP and Retained On-Site (ft3/SLDM-acre)

Name: Annual Runoff Volume Treated and Discharged
Description: Annual Runoff Volume Captured by the BMP, Treated and Discharged (ft3/SLDM-acre)

Name: Annual Runoff Volume Bypassed Without Treatment
Description: Annual Runoff Volume Not Captured by the BMP (ft3/SLDM-acre)
